headline: ADP Nominates Karen S. Lynch and Robert H. Swan to Board of Directors
summary: ADP (Nasdaq: ADP), a global leader in HR and payroll solutions, announced today that Karen S. Lynch and Robert H. Swan have been nominated to the Board of Directors in connection with ADP's Annual Meeting of Stockholders, set for November 12, 2025.
